<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Strict//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-strict.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
  <head>
    <title>CSS Writing Modes Test: text baseline alignment - text including different font size (alphabetical alignment with horizontal layout)</title>
    <link rel="author" title="Hajime Shiozawa" href="mailto:hajime.shiozawa@gmail.com" />
    <link rel="help" title="CSS3 Writing modes: 4.4. Baseline Alignment" href="http://www.w3.org/TR/css3-writing-modes/#baseline-alignment" />
    <link rel="match" href="text-baseline-004-ref.xht" />
    <meta name="assert" content="This test checks the generation of text baseline with different font size. When 'writing-mode' is horizontal, then the alphabetical baseline is used as the dominant baseline." />
    <meta name="flags" content="image" />
    <style type="text/css"><![CDATA[
      div > p, p#control {
        font-size: 2em;
        background-color: orange;
      }
      img {
        margin-left: -210px;
      }

      /* writing-mode property */
      .horizontal-tb {
        writing-mode: horizontal-tb;
      }

      /* text-orientation property */
      .mixed {
        text-orientation: mixed;
      }
      .upright {
        text-orientation: upright;
      }
      .sideways-right {
        text-orientation: sideways-right;
      }
      .sideways-left {
        text-orientation: sideways-left;
      }
      .sideways {
        text-orientation: sideways;
      }
      .use-glyph-orientation {
        text-orientation: use-glyph-orientation;
      }

      /* font */
      .font-size-large {
        font-size: 1.5em;
      }
      .font-size-small {
        font-size: 0.75em;
      }
  ]]></style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>Test passes if ...</p>
    <ol>
      <li>the bottom of glyph 'L' is touching a thin blue line in each 7 orange rectangles and</li>
      <li>all 7 orange rectangles are <strong>identical</strong>.</li>
    </ol>

    <p id="control">LLL<span class='font-size-large'>LL</span><span class='font-size-small'>LL</span>LLL<img src="support/blue-horiz-line-220x1.png" alt="Image download support must be enabled" /></p>

    <div class="horizontal-tb">
      <p class="mixed">LLL<span class='font-size-large'>LL</span><span class='font-size-small'>LL</span>LLL<img src="./support/blue-horiz-line-220x1.png" alt="Image download support must be enabled" /></p>
      <p class="upright">LLL<span class='font-size-large'>LL</span><span class='font-size-small'>LL</span>LLL<img src="./support/blue-horiz-line-220x1.png" alt="Image download support must be enabled" /></p>
      <p class="sideways-right">LLL<span class='font-size-large'>LL</span><span class='font-size-small'>LL</span>LLL<img src="./support/blue-horiz-line-220x1.png" alt="Image download support must be enabled" /></p>
      <p class="sideways-left">LLL<span class='font-size-large'>LL</span><span class='font-size-small'>LL</span>LLL<img src="./support/blue-horiz-line-220x1.png" alt="Image download support must be enabled" /></p>
      <p class="sideways">LLL<span class='font-size-large'>LL</span><span class='font-size-small'>LL</span>LLL<img src="./support/blue-horiz-line-220x1.png" alt="Image download support must be enabled" /></p>
      <p class="use-glyph-orientation">LLL<span class='font-size-large'>LL</span><span class='font-size-small'>LL</span>LLL<img src="./support/blue-horiz-line-220x1.png" alt="Image download support must be enabled" /></p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
